OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has again
OL,7,Ftaken aim at the UK's military support
OL,8,Fin the Middle East, denigrating its
OL,9,Faircraft carriers, HMS Queen Elizabeth
OL,10,Fand HMS Prince of Wales, as "toys".
OL,12,FSpeaking at the start of a White House
OL,13,FCabinet meeting on Thursday, Trump
OL,14,Fcriticised the speed at which the UK
OL,15,Fsent help in the days following the
OL,16,Fjoint Israeli-US attacks on Iran
OL,17,Falmost one month ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,F"We had the UK say that 'we'll send' `
OL,7,Fthis is three weeks ago ` 'we'll send
OL,8,Four aircraft carriers', which aren't
OL,9,Fthe best aircraft carriers by the
OL,10,Fway," he said. "They're toys compared
OL,11,Fto what we have."
OL,13,F"But 'we'll send our aircraft carrier
OL,14,Fwhen the war is over'. I said 'Oh
OL,15,Fthat's wonderful, thank you very much.
OL,16,FDon't bother. We don't need it,'" he
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,FHe also directed part of his tirade,
OL,7,Fonce again, at Prime Minister Keir
OL,8,FStarmer, saying: "I think he's a
OL,9,Flovely man, but I think he did
OL,10,Fsomething that was shocking. He didn't
OL,11,Fwant to help us."
OL,13,FThe US president, however, denied that
OL,14,Fthe transatlantic tensions would
OL,15,Faffect the King's planned visit to the
OL,16,FUS, insisting that it would go ahead.
OL,18,F"He's going to be here very soon, as
OL,19,Fyou know, we're going have a state
OL,20,Fdinner," he said. "It's going be
OL,21,Fgreat," he added.
OL,26,@pD@ROUsD@QO]zD@AOU|D@HO]|D@SOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,FThere have been calls for the historic
OL,7,Froyal trip to be scrapped or delayed
OL,8,Fbecause of the ongoing Middle East
OL,9,Fcrisis.
OL,11,FThe tour has yet to be officially
OL,12,Fannounced, but the King and Queen are
OL,13,Fexpected to visit Washington and New
OL,14,FYork in April to mark the 250th
OL,15,Fanniversary of American independence.
OL,17,FTrump also lashed out at NATO allies,
OL,18,Fsaying they did "absolutely nothing"
OL,19,Fto help the US in the ongoing conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,F"Now they all want to help. When
OL,7,Fthey're annihilated, the other side is
OL,8,Fannihilated; they will say, 'we'd love
OL,9,Fto send ships,'" he said.
OL,11,FThis is not the first time the US
OL,12,Fpresident has critiqued the UK's
OL,13,Fmilitary capabilities or its lack of
OL,14,Finvolvement in the ongoing conflict.
OL,16,FEarlier this month, Trump told
OL,17,Freporters Sir Keir Starmer is "no
OL,18,FWinston Churchill" after the PM
OL,19,Frefused to permit the use of UK bases
OL,20,Ffor the first strikes on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,FThe US had wanted to use the military
OL,7,Fbase in Diego Garcia on the Chagos
OL,8,FIslands, but Starmer said bases should
OL,9,Fonly be used for defensive purposes.
OL,11,FTrump told journalists that he was
OL,12,F"not happy with the UK" as a result of
OL,13,Fthe decision.
OL,15,FSpeaking at a press conference later,
OL,16,FStarmer said the "special
OL,17,Frelationship" with the US "remains
OL,18,Fintact", despite the ongoing criticism
OL,19,Ffrom Trump.
OL,26,@yD@MO]yD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,FThe UK government later agreed to
OL,7,Fallow the US military to use the UK
OL,8,Fbases in operations to prevent Iran
OL,9,Fattacking ships in the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz.
OL,12,FPermission was only granted for
OL,13,Fspecific strikes tied to shipping, in
OL,14,Fan effort to protect boats in the
OL,15,Fvital oil shipping channel.
OL,17,FThis was seen as a defensive
OL,18,Foperation, as opposed to encouraging
OL,19,Fescalation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
