PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSince then, on Monday, Starmer was
OL,12,Fasked by MP Meg Hillier how he deals
OL,13,Fwith Trump who could be "quite rude"
OL,14,Fabout the UK.
OL,16,FThe prime minister replied:
OL,17,F"Notwithstanding the pressure that
OL,18,Fcomes from elsewhere, I will remain
OL,19,Flaser-focused on what is in the
OL,20,FBritish national interest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774605947
OL,3,CTrump says UK aircraft carriers are
OL,4,C'toys' compared to US ones
OL,6,F"And a lot of what is said or done is
OL,7,Fundoubtedly said or done to put
OL,8,Fpressure on me. I have no doubt about
OL,9,Fthat. I understand exactly what is
OL,10,Fgoing on, but I'm not going to be
OL,11,Fwavering on this."
OL,13,F"I'm the British prime minister and my
OL,14,Fjob is to be absolutely focused on
OL,15,Fwhat's in the British national
OL,16,Finterest", he added.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
